  23 Jun 2007; Petteri Räty <betelgeuse@gentoo.org>
  files/cpuid-fomit-frame-pointer.patch, files/dynamic-libstdc++.patch,
  files/gettimeofday-declaration.patch, openjdk-1.7.0.0_alpha14.ebuild:
  Add back keywords as this works just fine when you build it against the same
  version of sun-jdk. Also comment on some patches about where they came from.

*openjdk-1.7.0.0_alpha14 (22 Jun 2007)

  22 Jun 2007; Petteri Räty <betelgeuse@gentoo.org> 
  +openjdk-1.7.0.0_alpha14.ebuild,
  +files/b14-gcc4.patch, +files/execstack.patch,
  +files/external-libXinerama.patch, +files/fontconfig-directlink.patch,
  +files/icedtea-text-relocations.patch, +files/tempname-free.patch:
  Version bump. Uses external libXinerama, fixes text relocations, can use
  fontconfig via direct linking instead of dlopening with the fontconfig USE
  flag.

  20 Jun 2007; Petteri Räty <betelgeuse@gentoo.org>
  +files/dynamic-libstdc++.patch, openjdk-1.7.0.0_alpha13.ebuild:
  Always link libstdc++ dynamically.

  08 Jun 2007; Petteri Räty <betelgeuse@gentoo.org>
  openjdk-1.7.0.0_alpha13.ebuild, +files/cpuid-fomit-frame-pointer.patch,
  files/external-zlib.patch, +files/external-zlib-splash.patch,
  files/gettimeofday-declaration.patch, files/lesstif.patch:
  Build and install platform javadocs with the doc use flag, enable user
  CFLAGS over build system, update the zlib patches to be split in two and
  make FULL_VERSION static so that ccache works properly.

  30 May 2007; Petteri Räty <betelgeuse@gentoo.org>
  openjdk-1.7.0.0_alpha13.ebuild:
  Fix jre/bin executable permission marking.

  27 May 2007; Petteri Räty <betelgeuse@gentoo.org>
  openjdk-1.7.0.0_alpha13.ebuild:
  My permission handling wasn't working for directories.

  26 May 2007; Petteri Räty <betelgeuse@gentoo.org>
  openjdk-1.7.0.0_alpha13.ebuild:
  cp even with -p seems to preserve permission so just chmod everything to 644
  after it.

  26 May 2007; Petteri Räty <betelgeuse@gentoo.org>
  -openjdk-1.7.0.0_alpha12-r1.ebuild:
  Remove old version.

  26 May 2007; Petteri Räty <betelgeuse@gentoo.org>
  openjdk-1.7.0.0_alpha13.ebuild:
  The permission fix wasn't matching jvm.cfg.

  26 May 2007; Petteri Räty <betelgeuse@gentoo.org>
  openjdk-1.7.0.0_alpha13.ebuild:
  My cleanup dropped external-libpng patch so it wasn't compiling.

  26 May 2007; Petteri Räty <betelgeuse@gentoo.org>
  openjdk-1.7.0.0_alpha13.ebuild:
  Revert user CFLAGS/CXXFLAGS pach as it makes the ebuild segmentation fault.

  26 May 2007; Petteri Räty <betelgeuse@gentoo.org>
  openjdk-1.7.0.0_alpha13.ebuild:
  Change sun-bcla to sun-prerelease-jdk7 as that's where we take our binary plug.

*openjdk-1.7.0.0_alpha13 (26 May 2007)

  26 May 2007; Petteri Räty <betelgeuse@gentoo.org>
  +openjdk-1.7.0.0_alpha13.ebuild, +files/gettimeofday-declaration.patch:
  Version bump.

  25 May 2007; Petteri Räty <betelgeuse@gentoo.org>
  openjdk-1.7.0.0_alpha12-r1.ebuild:
  Bring in matching version of sun-jdk so the the binary parts stay in sync.

*openjdk-1.7.0.0_alpha12-r1 (24 May 2007)

  24 May 2007; Petteri Räty <betelgeuse@gentoo.org>
  -openjdk-1.7.0.0_alpha12.ebuild, +openjdk-1.7.0.0_alpha12-r1.ebuild:
  Revision bump to push out accumulated fixes.

  24 May 2007; Petteri Räty <betelgeuse@gentoo.org>
  openjdk-1.7.0.0_alpha12.ebuild, +files/noundef.patch:
  Link dynamically against libstdc++.

  22 May 2007; Petteri Räty <betelgeuse@gentoo.org>
  openjdk-1.7.0.0_alpha12.ebuild:
  Fix permission issue. For some reason for some people OpenJDK is getting
  build with permission mask 600.

  21 May 2007; Petteri Räty <betelgeuse@gentoo.org>
  openjdk-1.7.0.0_alpha12.ebuild:
  Add DEPEND on app-arch/unzip  and app-arch/zip.

  20 May 2007; Petteri Räty <betelgeuse@gentoo.org>
  openjdk-1.7.0.0_alpha12.ebuild, +files/external-giflib.patch,
  +files/external-jpeg-splash.patch, +files/external-libpng.patch:
  Use the system installed copy of libpng instead of the bundled one.

  15 May 2007; Petteri Räty <betelgeuse@gentoo.org>
  openjdk-1.7.0.0_alpha12.ebuild:
  Remove the need for dev-java/ant by running make directly.

  13 May 2007; Petteri Räty <betelgeuse@gentoo.org>
  openjdk-1.7.0.0_alpha12.ebuild:
  Fix GPL-2-with-classpath-exception to GPL-2-with-linking-exception

  13 May 2007; Petteri Räty <betelgeuse@gentoo.org>
  openjdk-1.7.0.0_alpha12.ebuild, +files/external-zlib.patch,
  +files/j2se-cxxflags.patch:
  Use system installed copy of zlib.

  10 May 2007; Petteri Räty <betelgeuse@gentoo.org>
  openjdk-1.7.0.0_alpha12.ebuild, +files/lesstif.patch:
  Add patch to build against lesstif.

  10 May 2007; Petteri Räty <betelgeuse@gentoo.org>
  openjdk-1.7.0.0_alpha12.ebuild:
  dev-libs/elfutils and media-libs/jpeg are not needed. Reasons in comments.
  Don't strip binaries.

  10 May 2007; Petteri Räty <betelgeuse@gentoo.org>
  openjdk-1.7.0.0_alpha12.ebuild:
  Work around argument list getting too long by renaming openjdk to o and
  don't RESTRICT stripping any more.

  09 May 2007; Petteri Räty <betelgeuse@gentoo.org>
  openjdk-1.7.0.0_alpha12.ebuild:
  Add DEPENDs gotten from included_headers.sh and fix src_install for amd64.

  09 May 2007; Petteri Räty <betelgeuse@gentoo.org>
  openjdk-1.7.0.0_alpha12.ebuild:
  Add libraries OpenJDK links against and don't RDEPEND on ant-core, sun-jdk,
  virtual/jdk or motif.

  09 May 2007; Miroslav Šulc <fordfrog@gentoo.org>
  openjdk-1.7.0.0_alpha12.ebuild:
  Fixed HOMEPAGE and access violation while creating /root/.openjdk

  08 May 2007; Petteri Räty <betelgeuse@gentoo.org>
  openjdk-1.7.0.0_alpha12.ebuild:
  Fix SRC_URI to include BASE_URL.

*openjdk-1.7.0.0_alpha12 (08 May 2007)

  08 May 2007; Petteri Räty <betelgeuse@gentoo.org>
  +openjdk-1.7.0.0_alpha12.ebuild, +files/openjdk-1.7.env:
  Add initial ebuild for openjdk. The build takes long.

